Litecoin,Global,is,an,online,exchange,that,allows,users,to,buy,or,issue,stocks,in,virtual,currency,companies,The,site,operates,entirely,on,Litecoin,which,users,must,purchase,from,exchanges,or,mine,themselves,The,LitecoinGlobal,API,allows,users,to,query,for,lists,of,all,assets,and,market,data,ticker,data,for,a,specific,asset,order,book,data,contract,data,all,trades,on,the,site,trade,history,dividends,as,well,as,full,account,and,portfolio,information,The,services,uses,REST,calls,and,can,return,JSON,or,CSV